column5: Happy new years everyone. Be safe and have a wonderful time. If you are at casino niagra to ring it in post back here we can have a beer.
Back at ya Jed.  Im fishing in the AM,so there,s no ringing in. Just like the last 20 or so years. Think I might of done one,but a tradition for me is,fish new years day.  All the best, to everyone .
All the greatest fishing and fortunes in 2013!
Happy New Year for all my OFC friends.
Another quiet New Years Eve at the Beans' household...  The kittens were busy tho...
All the best in 2013 to OFC members!  Bring on the ice!!
